metric_name: Total Gross Revenue (Booked/Billed, ADPT, FY2025, Excl. MRCA, Excl. Zero/Near-Zero, Un-invoiced)
business_description: The sum of gross revenue amounts for transactions that are 'Booked' or 'Billed', originate from the 'ADPT' system, are for financial year 2025, exclude 'Medium Rare Content Agency', have an invoice number of '-1' (likely un-invoiced), and are not near zero.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(t0.gross_revenue_amount) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_advertising.v_adsales_revenue_client` AS t0 WHERE (t0.revenue_transaction_status IN ('Booked', 'Billed') AND (t0.source_publishing_division != 'Medium Rare Content Agency' OR t0.source_publishing_division IS NULL) AND t0.source_system_code IN ('ADPT') AND t0.invoice_number = '-1' AND NOT(t0.gross_revenue_amount BETWEEN -1.000000 AND 1.000000) AND t0.financial_year IN ('2025'))

metric_name: Total Gross Revenue by Financial Year, Week, Source System (Booked/Billed, FY2025, Excl. MRCA, Un-invoiced)
business_description: The sum of gross revenue amounts, grouped by financial year, financial week, and source system code, for transactions that are 'Booked' or 'Billed', exclude 'Medium Rare Content Agency', have an invoice number of '-1' (likely un-invoiced), and are for financial year 2025 from specific source systems.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.financial_year, SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_week AS INT64) AS financial_week_id, t0.source_system_code, SUM(t0.gross_revenue_amount) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_advertising.v_adsales_revenue_client` AS t0 WHERE (t0.revenue_transaction_status IN ('Booked', 'Billed') AND (t0.source_publishing_division != 'Medium Rare Content Agency' OR t0.source_publishing_division IS NULL) AND t0.invoice_number = '-1' AND t0.source_system_code IN ('PLUTO', 'CPQ', 'ADPT') AND t0.financial_year IN ('2025')) GROUP BY t0.financial_year, financial_week_id, t0.source_system_code

metric_name: Sum of Financial Week ID (Booked/Billed, FY2025, Excl. MRCA, Un-invoiced)
business_description: The sum of financial week IDs, grouped by financial year, financial week, and source system code, for transactions that are 'Booked' or 'Billed', exclude 'Medium Rare Content Agency', have an invoice number of '-1' (likely un-invoiced), and are for financial year 2025 from specific source systems. This is an unusual aggregation, possibly used for ordering or internal calculation.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.financial_year, SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_week AS INT64) AS financial_week_id, t0.source_system_code, SUM(SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_week AS INT64)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_advertising.v_adsales_revenue_client` AS t0 WHERE (t0.revenue_transaction_status IN ('Booked', 'Billed') AND (t0.source_publishing_division != 'Medium Rare Content Agency' OR t0.source_publishing_division IS NULL) AND t0.invoice_number = '-1' AND t0.source_system_code IN ('PLUTO', 'CPQ', 'ADPT') AND t0.financial_year IN ('2025')) GROUP BY t0.financial_year, financial_week_id, t0.source_system_code

metric_name: Record Count by OS Level 5 (Fiscal Week 202548-202551)
business_description: The count of records from the finance operating statement, grouped by 'os_level_5', for specific fiscal weeks at the end of 2025.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.os_level_5, COUNT(1) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.prstn_finance_persisted.finance_operating_statement` AS t0 WHERE t0.fiscal_week_id IN ('202548', '202549', '202550', '202551') GROUP BY t0.os_level_5

metric_name: Data Load Timestamp (Excl. Digital Revenue Type)
business_description: The truncated data load timestamp, used as a dimension, for revenue transactions that are not classified as 'Digital' revenue.
sql_logic: SELECT DATETIME_TRUNC(t0.data_load_datetime, SECOND) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_advertising.v_adsales_revenue_client` AS t0 WHERE (t0.revenue_type NOT IN ('Digital') OR t0.revenue_type IS NULL) GROUP BY DATETIME_TRUNC(t0.data_load_datetime, SECOND)

metric_name: Total SS LGB by Advertiser, Booking, Publication (CW Media, SUDDENLY Pubs)
business_description: The sum of 'ss_lgb' (likely a revenue or booking amount), grouped by advertiser name, booking line number, booking number, financial month, revenue transaction status, and unified publication name, specifically for 'CW Media Pty Ltd' and 'SUDDENLY.CW' or 'SUDDENLY.NORTH' publications.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.advertiser_name, t0.booking_line_number, t0.booking_number, SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_month AS FLOAT64) AS financial_month_id, t0.revenue_transaction_status, t0.unified_publication_name, SUM(t0.ss_lgb) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_advertising.v_adsales_revenue_client` AS t0 WHERE (t0.advertiser_name IN ('CW Media Pty Ltd') AND t0.unified_publication_name IN ('SUDDENLY.CW', 'SUDDENLY.NORTH')) GROUP BY t0.advertiser_name, t0.booking_line_number, t0.booking_number, financial_month_id, t0.revenue_transaction_status, t0.unified_publication_name

metric_name: Data Load Timestamp (Filtered by Unified Publication GL Code)
business_description: The truncated data load timestamp, used as a dimension, for transactions associated with specific unified publication GL codes.
sql_logic: SELECT DATETIME_TRUNC(t0.data_load_datetime, SECOND) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_advertising.v_adsales_revenue_client` AS t0 WHERE t0.unified_publication_gl_code IN ('9707', '9655', '9658') GROUP BY DATETIME_TRUNC(t0.data_load_datetime, SECOND)

business_description: Volume added to subscriptions within a period.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(add_volume AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_add_volume FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: The name of the subscription category.
sql_logic: SELECT DISTINCT category_name FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` LIMIT 100;

business_description: The total number of subscriptions at the end of a fiscal period.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(closing_base AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_closing_base FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: The revenue earned from subscriptions.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(earned_amount AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_earned_amount FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: Identifier for the fiscal week (YYYYWW format).
sql_logic: SELECT DISTINCT fiscal_week_id FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` ORDER BY fiscal_week_id DESC LIMIT 100;

business_description: General Ledger publication code associated with subscriptions.
sql_logic: SELECT DISTINCT gl_publication_code FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` LIMIT 100;

business_description: The total number of subscriptions at the beginning of a fiscal period.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(opening_base AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_opening_base FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: Volume reduced from subscriptions within a period.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(red_volume AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_red_volume FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: Volume of subscriptions transferred into the current category/publication.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(transfer_in AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_transfer_in FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: Volume of subscriptions transferred out of the current category/publication.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(transfer_out AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_transfer_out FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_subscriptions` WHERE fiscal_week_id IN (202535) LIMIT 1;

business_description: General Ledger account identifier for digital subscription estimates.
sql_logic: SELECT DISTINCT gl_acc FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_gr_digsubs_estimate` LIMIT 100;

business_description: Distribution channel for circulation actuals.
sql_logic: SELECT DISTINCT channel FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_circulation_actuals` LIMIT 100;

business_description: Amount charged for home delivery of circulation items.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(home_del_charge AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_home_del_charge FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_circulation_actuals` LIMIT 1;

business_description: Credit amount issued for returned circulation items.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(returns_credit_amount AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_returns_credit_amount FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_circulation_actuals` LIMIT 1;

business_description: Adjustments made to circulation revenue.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_CAST(rev_adjust AS BIGNUMERIC)) AS total_rev_adjust FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_circulation_actuals` LIMIT 1;

business_description: Geographical state associated with circulation actuals.
sql_logic: SELECT DISTINCT state FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.sbx_fda_corefin.dv_tm1_pbf_circulation_actuals` LIMIT 100;

business_description: The total difference in gross amount, representing revenue movement. This is the core financial measure.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(t0.GROSS_AMOUNT_DIFF) AS total_gross_amount_diff FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 WHERE t0.movement_date = CURRENT_DATE()

business_description: The gross amount difference specifically for revenue classified as 'DIGITAL' by revenue type.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t0.revenue_type = 'DIGITAL' THEN t0.GROSS_AMOUNT_DIFF ELSE 0 END) AS digital_gross_amount_diff FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 WHERE t0.movement_date = CURRENT_DATE()

business_description: The gross amount difference specifically for revenue classified as 'PRINT' by revenue type.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t0.revenue_type = 'PRINT' THEN t0.GROSS_AMOUNT_DIFF ELSE 0 END) AS print_gross_amount_diff FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 WHERE t0.movement_date = CURRENT_DATE()

business_description: A custom categorization of revenue based on xtend_flag, revenue_sub_type, and revenue_type, grouping into 'XTEND', 'PROGRAMMATIC', 'ADPT DIGITAL', 'SUNDRY', or the original revenue_sub_type.
sql_logic: SELECT CASE WHEN (t0.xtend_flag = 'Y') THEN 'XTEND' WHEN (SAFE.LEFT(t0.revenue_sub_type, 3) = 'PRO' OR (t0.portfolio_parent_group_name_sync = 'DIGITAL OTHER' AND t0.revenue_sub_type = 'DIGITAL')) THEN 'PROGRAMMATIC' WHEN (t0.revenue_sub_type = 'DIGITAL') THEN 'ADPT DIGITAL' WHEN (SAFE.LEFT(t0.revenue_sub_type, 6) = 'SUNDRY') THEN 'SUNDRY' ELSE t0.revenue_sub_type END AS revenue_category FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The advertiser group, with NULL values replaced by 'Nah' for consistent reporting.
sql_logic: SELECT CASE WHEN t0.advertiser_group IS NULL THEN 'Nah' ELSE t0.advertiser_group END AS advertiser_group_handled FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The calculated start date of the financial month, derived from financial year and short month.
sql_logic: SELECT PARSE_DATE('%Y-%b-%d', CONCAT(SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_year AS STRING),'-',SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_short_month AS STRING),'-1')) AS financial_month_start_date FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The financial year associated with the revenue movement.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.financial_year FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The specific date of the revenue movement.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.movement_date FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The synchronized name of the parent portfolio group.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.portfolio_parent_group_name_sync FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The synchronized name of the Sales Segment General Manager.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.sales_segment_gm_name_sync FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The parent advertiser entity.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.advertiser_parent FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: Unique identifier for a booking line item.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.booking_line_id FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The unique identifier for a booking.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.booking_number FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The abbreviated name of the financial month.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.financial_short_month FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The synchronized name of the portfolio group.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.portfolio_group_name_sync FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The detailed sub-type of revenue.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.revenue_sub_type FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The high-level type of revenue (e.g., DIGITAL, PRINT).
sql_logic: SELECT t0.revenue_type FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: A flag indicating if the revenue is associated with XTEND.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.xtend_flag FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The group of the publishing division.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.publishing_division_group FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: The synchronized conformed name of the portfolio.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.portfolio_conformed_name_sync FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.revenue_movement` AS t0 LIMIT 1

business_description: Categorization of products offered.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.product_group FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The standardized name of the publication.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.unified_publication_name FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The parent division responsible for publishing.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.publishing_division_parent FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Synchronized sales segment name for General Managers.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.sales_segment_gm_name_sync FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Abbreviated financial month.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.financial_short_month FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The financial year.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.financial_year FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The financial quarter.
sql_logic: SELECT SAFE_CAST(t0.financial_quarter AS INT64) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Ordered financial month for sorting purposes.
sql_logic: SELECT CASE WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Jul') THEN '1.Jul' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Aug') THEN '2.Aug' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Sep') THEN '3.Sep' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Oct') THEN '4.Oct' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Nov') THEN '5.Nov' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Dec') THEN '6.Dec' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Jan') THEN '7.Jan' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Feb') THEN '8.Feb' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Mar') THEN '9.Mar' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Apr') THEN '10.Apr' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'May') THEN '11.May' WHEN (t0.financial_short_month = 'Jun') THEN '12.Jun' ELSE NULL END FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Categorization of revenue, with 'XTEND' flag overriding revenue type.
sql_logic: SELECT CASE WHEN (t0.xtend_flag = 'Y') THEN 'XTEND' ELSE t0.revenue_type END FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Offset of the financial month relative to a reference point (e.g., current month is 0).
sql_logic: SELECT t0.relative_fy_month_offset FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Offset of the financial year relative to a reference point (e.g., current year is 0, previous is -1).
sql_logic: SELECT t0.relative_fy_year_offset FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Synchronized sales segment name at Level 2.
sql_logic: SELECT t0.sales_segment_l_2_name_sync FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Flag indicating if the sales segment is 'Digital Other'. Used as a boolean measure.
sql_logic: SELECT MAX(t0.sales_segment_l_2_name_sync = 'Digital Other') FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The sum of all gross revenue amounts.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(t0.gross_revenue_amount) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the current financial year (relative_fy_year_offset = 0).
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the current financial year, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the previous financial year (relative_fy_year_offset = -1).
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = -1 THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the previous financial year, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = -1 THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the next financial year, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 1 THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the current financial year, excluding future periods, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN (t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 AND t0.is_future_period_flag = 'N') THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the previous financial year, conditional on a complex date logic involving fixed dates and digital revenue types.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN (t0.relative_fy_year_offset = -1 AND (SAFE_CAST(CASE WHEN (t0.revenue_type = 'DIGITAL' AND t0.revenue_group_subtype = 'DIGITAL' AND t0.sales_segment_l_2_name_sync = 'Digital Other' AND t0.advertiser_parent != 'DOUBLECLICK') THEN t0.fix_date_lod ELSE PARSE_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', t0.booking_line_created_date) END AS DATETIME) <= DATETIME_ADD(SAFE_CAST(DATE(TIMESTAMP '2025-01-06 02:37:12.747676+00', 'UTC') AS DATETIME), INTERVAL -365 DAY))) THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Gross revenue for the previous financial year, conditional on a complex date logic involving fixed dates and digital revenue types, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN (t0.relative_fy_year_offset = -1 AND (SAFE_CAST(CASE WHEN (t0.revenue_type = 'DIGITAL' AND t0.revenue_group_subtype = 'DIGITAL' AND t0.sales_segment_l_2_name_sync = 'Digital Other' AND t0.advertiser_parent != 'DOUBLECLICK') THEN t0.fix_date_lod ELSE PARSE_DATE('%Y-%m-%d', t0.booking_line_created_date) END AS DATETIME) <= DATETIME_ADD(SAFE_CAST(DATE(TIMESTAMP '2025-01-06 02:37:12.747676+00', 'UTC') AS DATETIME), INTERVAL -365 DAY))) THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The sum of all Sales Segment Last Good Booking amounts.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(t0.ss_lgb) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Sales Segment Last Good Booking for the current financial year, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 THEN t0.ss_lgb ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Sales Segment Last Good Booking for the current financial year, specifically for past weeks (relative_fy_week_offset < 0).
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 AND t0.relative_fy_week_offset < 0 THEN t0.ss_lgb ELSE 0 END) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: Calculated Sales Segment Last Good Booking for the current financial year and current week, based on DOW_Today.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 AND t0.relative_fy_week_offset = 0 THEN SAFE_DIVIDE(t0.ss_lgb * t0.DOW_Today, 7) ELSE 0 END) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The sum of all pipeline amounts.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(t0.pipeline) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

metric_name: Current FY Revenue vs SS_LGB Delta (k)
business_description: The difference between current FY gross revenue and current FY SS_LGB, in thousands.
sql_logic: SELECT SUM(SAFE_DIVIDE(CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 THEN t0.gross_revenue_amount ELSE 0 END - CASE WHEN t0.relative_fy_year_offset = 0 THEN t0.ss_lgb ELSE 0 END, 1000)) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The maximum relative financial month offset observed in the data.
sql_logic: SELECT MAX(t0.relative_fy_month_offset) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0

business_description: The maximum relative financial year offset observed in the data.
sql_logic: SELECT MAX(t0.relative_fy_year_offset) FROM `ncau-data-newsquery-prd.asl_finance_derived.adsales_performance` AS t0
